                <textLang mainLang="syr"/>
                <note type="disambiguation">The Epistle of Baruch is sometimes attached to 2 Baruch (Apocalypse of Baruch) as 
                    78:1–87:1. In the Syriac tradition, it is sometimes referred to as the "First Epistle of Baruch." This should not be 
                    confused with the work known in Western usage as <title>1 Baruch<ptr target="http://syriaca.org/work/67"/></title>, which in Syriac may go by the 
                    title "Second Epistle of Baruch."</note>
